column1: They are removing the touchbar from #macbook & im not happy about it. I don't understand why they keep switching around.
Did Cristiano Ronaldo really just put those Coke bottles aside?
The battery of the #Apple Macbook Pro 16 inch is so good that I can keep using it all night.
$2400 for a base model? No thank you
It took me 2 hours to change my country setting in Google Play. What a mess!
